    "asOf": "2021-04-15",
    "date": "2021-06-21T18:50:27Z",
    "text": "Palomares Veterans Act of 2021\n\nThis bill includes veterans who participated in the cleanup of radioactive materials at Palomares, Spain, as radiation-exposed veterans for purposes of the Department of Veterans Affairs presumption of service-connection for specified cancers.\n\nUnder a presumption of service-connection, specific disabilities diagnosed in certain veterans are presumed to have been caused by the circumstances of their military service. Health care benefits and disability compensation may then be awarded."
  },
